data.description: This home is situated on a CUL-DE-SAC and backs to a GREEN BELT. The home welcomes you with a covered front porch. As you walk in you will see the high ceiling and the double sided fireplace. Off the kitchen you will find a utility room, a pantry the door leading to the beautifully LANDSCAPED back yard. The patio is bigger than the average home in this area. The upper level includes 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. One in the master bedroom. This home also has a FULL BASEMENT!! Carpets, air ducts and dryer hose have been professionally cleaned. The AC keeps you cool in the summer.
